Package com.joliciel.talismane.extensions

Entry point package for extensions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Extensions
    Extensions use a command-line identical to TalismaneMain.

    To use extensions, various configuration settings need to be updated to refer to the classes in this package, and in some cases fill in their specific configuration settings.
